  <section class="section section--gray">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;">
        <div class="text-center mb-48">
          <span class="section-label">Frequently Asked Questions</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">Questions About Leaving a Google Review</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-list">

          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
              How do I leave a Google review for a small business?
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>On your phone: open Google Maps, search for the business, tap their listing, scroll to Reviews, and tap "Write a review." On desktop: search Google, find the Knowledge Panel on the right, and click "Write a review." The whole process takes about two minutes.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
              Do I need a Google account to leave a review?
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>Yes. You need a free Google account to post a review. You can create one at accounts.google.com — you don't need to use it for email. Reviews can't be submitted without an account.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
              How much does a Google review actually help a small business?
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>Reviews are one of the strongest signals Google uses to rank local businesses in the Map Pack — the top 3 results that appear when someone searches for a local service. A business with 20 genuine reviews will consistently outrank an identical business with zero reviews. For small independents competing against national chains, this is often the deciding factor.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
              How do I leave a review specifically for Riverside Auto Rental?
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>Search for "Riverside Auto Rental Black River Falls" in Google Maps or Google Search, click the listing, scroll to Reviews, and click "Write a review." You can also call us at <a href="tel:+17153961466" style="color:var(--navy);">715-396-1466</a> and we'll text you a direct link.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

